---
import Heading from '../components/Heading.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="flex flex-col">
    <Heading title="About me" textGradient size="h2" />
    <p class="text-xl">
      I'm a web developer passionate about technology and programming. I'm
      currently working as a frontend developer at <a
        href="https://softtek.com"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-blue-400">Softtek</a
      >
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 text-justify md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-10">
        <li>
          <img
            src="/logos/astro-logo-light.png"
            alt="astro"
            class="m-auto hidden h-32 w-32 object-contain dark:block"
          />
          <img
            src="/logos/astro-logo-dark.png"
            alt="astro"
            class="m-auto block h-32 w-32 object-contain dark:hidden"
          />
          <p>
            I fell in love with this new framework that help us to do things
            faster and with a great performance, I use it a lot to make static
            web pages like my own site and a portfolio, also a landing page and
            more! ðŸš€
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://swift.org" target="_blank">
            <img
              src="/logos/swift-dark.svg"
              alt="swift"
              class="m-auto hidden h-32 w-32 object-contain dark:block"
            />
            <img
              src="/logos/swift-light.svg"
              alt="swift"
              class="m-auto block h-32 w-32 object-contain dark:hidden"
            />
          </a>
          <p>
            To develop my apps for iOS natively and to complement my knowledge
            about mobile developing
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://reactnative.dev">
            <img
              src="/logos/react-native.svg"
              alt="React native"
              class="m-auto h-32 w-32 object-contain"
            /></a
          >
          <p>
            To create awesome apps for Android and iOS using JavaScript or
            TypeScript!
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
